| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2102 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1fba5e79-5e94-5c81-be33-64f5ae69b30c"
